recoveryPasswordDescription:
Faka iphasiwedi yakho yokufumana kwakhona ukuze ufake iakhawunti yakho kwizixhobo ezintsha.

Iakhawunti yakho ayinakufumaneka ngaphandle kwephasiwedi yakho yokufumana kwakhona. Qinisekisa ukuba iyonke indawo ekhuselekileyo kwaye ungayabelani nabani na.

recoveryPasswordHidePermanentlyDescripti:
Ngaphandle kwegama lakho eligqithisiweyo lokubuyisela, awukwazi ukulayisha iakhawunti yakho kwizixhobo ezintsha.

Sikugxininise kakhulu ukuba ugcine igama lakho lokubuyisela kwindawo ekhuselekileyo neyimfihlo phambi kokuqhubeka.
Uqinisekile ukuba ufuna ukufihla rhoqo iphasiwedi yakho yokubuyisela kule sixhobo? Oku akunakubuyiselwa.
